		<technology>
			<technologicalApplicability xml:lang="en">The described industrial process involves the recycling and treatment of materials for the manufacturing of multi-crystalline silicon photovoltaic (multi-Si PV) modules. Specifically, glass is remelted, ethylene vinyl acetate (EVA) undergoes thermal treatment, and aluminum is subject to remelting and chemical processing to allow their use as substitutes for virgin materials in the assembly of PV modules. Chemical treatments are also necessary for the recycling of silicon and silver as part of the production process for polysilicon and multi-Si PV cells.</technologicalApplicability>
			<technologicalApplicability xml:lang="zh">所描述的工业过程包括回收和处理用于制造多晶硅光伏（multi-Si PV）组件的材料。具体来说，玻璃需要重熔，乙烯醋酸乙烯（EVA）需经热处理，铝要经过重熔和化学处理，以便它们可以用作光伏模块装配中原始材料的替代品。硅和银的回收也需要化学处理，作为多晶硅生产和多硅光伏电池生产过程的一部分。</technologicalApplicability>
			<referenceToTechnologyFlowDiagrammOrPicture type="source data set" refObjectId="96ebf9c9-18bd-6e9c-1b4a-db9447d9b728" uri="../sources/96ebf9c9-18bd-6e9c-1b4a-db9447d9b728.xml">
				<common:shortDescription xml:lang="en">OzRub6G6MoJYs1xvNxUcdxTynnh.png</common:shortDescription>
			</referenceToTechnologyFlowDiagrammOrPicture>
		</technology>
	</processInformation>
